  m_GameObject: {fileID: 993948843}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: ea1c59ace054e0f4cb9e17e1e77a9b89, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueTrigger
  textComponent: {fileID: 0}
  lines:
  - '[ Outside the Temple ]'
  - She came out into the dusk.
  - 'The sky was the colour of everything at once: the deep gold of sunlight the
    violet of the desert at day''s end, the burning amber of a world that had nearly
    lost something irreplaceable and had been given it back.'
  - Nesia stood at the temple steps and breathed.
  - "The pen was almost turning dark. The glow was nearly gone. She looked down at
    it \u2014 her constant companion through every trial, every puzzle, every moment
    of doubt and every moment of clarity \u2014 and felt something very close to
    grief."
  textSpeed: 0.05
  playerTag: Player
  triggerOnce: 1
