--- !u!114 &1334199985
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1334199981}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: ea1c59ace054e0f4cb9e17e1e77a9b89, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueTrigger
  textComponent: {fileID: 0}
  lines:
  - As she walked, something began to change.
  - "Not dramatically. The sun \u2014 which had been sinking \u2014 simply held.
    For one long, extraordinary moment, the light did not move. The shadows did not
    lengthen. "
  - 'Nesia felt something she had felt only once before: a warmth in the centre of
    her chest. A pressure. Like a hand, vast and gentle, placed briefly over her
    heart.'
  - '"...Who am I? I don''t understand why I was brought back. Why me?"'
  - The warmth deepened. And for the first and only time, the sky spoke.
  textSpeed: 0.05
  playerTag: Player
  triggerOnce: 1
